return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.1','translation-revision-date'=>'2025-09-05 08:22:00+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Plugins - CF7 Apps – [Honeypot and hCAPTCHA for Contact Form 7] - Stable (latest release)','language'=>'zh_TW','messages'=>['CF7Apps\' Honeypot App.'=>'CF7Apps 的誘捕功能。','We\'ve moved your Honeypot settings to the Honeypot App in CF7Apps. You can still use both, but we recommend using the'=>'我們已將誘捕功能設定移至 CF7Apps 的 [誘捕功能] 分頁中。目前仍可以使用這兩個不同位置的設定頁面，但是我們建議使用','Welcome to CF7Apps!'=>'歡迎使用 CF7Apps！','No'=>'否','Yes'=>'是','Add Contact Form'=>'新增聯絡表單','Contact Forms'=>'Contact Forms','All Apps'=>'全部功能','Install Contact Form 7'=>'安裝 Contact Form 7','%s requires Contact Form 7 to be installed and activated. %s'=>'%s 需要先安裝並啟用 Contact Form 7。%s','Time Check Value (Seconds)'=>'時間檢查值 (秒)','If checked, the accessibility label will not be generated. This is not recommended, but may improve.'=>'啟用這項功能後，便不會產生無障礙功能標籤。不建議這麼做，但可能會加強封鎖。','By default Honeypot uses inline CSS on the honeypot field to hide it. Checking this box moves.'=>'依照預設，誘捕功能會將內嵌 CSS 套用至 [誘捕功能] 欄位以隱藏該欄位。啟用這項設定便能移動 CSS。','To assure the honeypot isn\'t auto-completed by a browser, we add an atypical "autocomplete" .'=>'為了確保瀏覽器不會自動完成 [誘捕功能] 欄位的填寫，外掛加入了非典型的 autocomplete 屬性值。','You can customize the (hidden) accessibility message, or just leave it the default value: Please leave this field empty.'=>'網站管理員可以自訂 (隱藏的) 無障礙功能訊息，或保留使用預設值 [請將這個欄位留空]。','(Recommended) By default the Honeypot field is not stored with other fields in form-saving plugins like Flamingo. However, saving the field can be useful to see what spam bots are leaving behind to help you improve your spam stopping superpowers. If you\'d like to store the value of the field, simply check this box (and install Flamingo).'=>'(建議使用) 依照預設，表單儲存外掛如 Flamingo，並不會儲存 [誘捕功能] 欄位的資料。不過，儲存 [誘捕功能] 欄位的資料會對檢視是哪些惡意檢索程式留下資料很有幫助，並且可以藉以改進阻擋濫填內容的能力。如果需要儲存 [誘捕功能] 欄位的資料，請啟用這項功能並安裝 Flamingo。','Enable Honeypot App'=>'啟用誘捕功能','Add invisible honeypot fields to your forms to trap spambots, ensuring spam-free form submission.'=>'在聯絡表單中新增隱形的 [誘捕功能] 欄位，便能攔截垃圾留言機器人，並確保不會提交含有垃圾訊息聯絡表單。','Choose the theme for the hCaptcha widget.'=>'選取 hCaptcha 小工具的外觀樣式。','Dark'=>'深色','Light'=>'淺色','Theme'=>'外觀樣式','Add custom CSS classes to the hCaptcha widget.'=>'新增自訂 CSS 類別至 hCaptcha 小工具。','Custom CSS'=>'自訂 CSS','Choose the size of the hCaptcha widget.'=>'設定 hCaptcha 小工具的尺寸。','Compact'=>'小巧','Normal'=>'標準','Size'=>'大小','Language'=>'語言','Error message'=>'錯誤訊息','Documentation'=>'線上說明','Need help setting this up? Check out our'=>'設定時如果需要協助，請參考我們的','Save Settings'=>'儲存設定','Choose a language for your CAPTCHA display.'=>'選取人機驗證要顯示的語言。','Force hCaptcha to render in a specific language.'=>'強制 hCaptcha 使用指定語言轉譯。','Enter a custom message to display when CAPTCHA validation fails.'=>'請輸入人機驗證失敗時要顯示的自訂訊息。','Invalid Captcha'=>'無效的人機驗證','Invalid Captcha error message'=>'無效的人機驗證的錯誤訊息','Enter your secret key. Don\'t have one? <a href="https://dashboard.hcaptcha.com/settings/secrets">Click here</a> to generate a new key.'=>'輸入專屬秘密金鑰。如果沒有秘密金鑰，請點擊<a href="https://dashboard.hcaptcha.com/settings/secrets" target="_blank">這裡</a>以產生金鑰。','Secret key is required.'=>'秘密金鑰為必要項目。','Secret Key'=>'秘密金鑰','Enter your site key. Don\'t have one? <a href="https://dashboard.hcaptcha.com/sites">Click here</a> to generate a new key.'=>'輸入專屬網站金鑰。如果沒有網站金鑰，請點擊<a href="https://dashboard.hcaptcha.com/sites" target="_blank">這裡</a>以產生金鑰。','Site key is required.'=>'網站金鑰為必要項目。','Site Key'=>'網站金鑰','Enable hCaptcha App'=>'啟用 hCaptcha 功能','hCaptcha Settings'=>'hCaptcha 設定','Spam Protection'=>'垃圾訊息保護','Add hCaptcha to Contact Form 7 for secure, spam-free forms.'=>'將 hCaptcha 人機驗證功能加入 Contact Form 7 中便能獲得安全性及沒有垃圾訊息的聯絡表單。','hCaptcha'=>'hCaptcha','Zulu'=>'祖魯文','Yoruba'=>'優魯巴文','Yiddish'=>'意第緒文','Xhosa'=>'廓薩文','Welsh'=>'威爾斯文','Vietnamese'=>'越南文','Uzbek'=>'烏茲別克文','Urdu'=>'烏都文','Ukrainian'=>'烏克蘭文','Uyghur'=>'維吾爾文','Turkmen'=>'土庫曼文','Turkish'=>'土耳其文','Thai'=>'泰文','Teluga'=>'泰盧固文',